=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104azy1665702712971.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/azy1665702712971.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/azy1665702712971.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"azy1665702712971\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Maximum Field Length </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The maximum number of characters allowed for data in this field. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"azy1665702712971__section_w2698ab1b5b1_w2699ab1b5_w2700ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"azy1665702712971__table_d815e1_d816e1_d817e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"azy1665702712971__table_d815e1_d816e1_d817e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"azy1665702712971__table_d815e1_d816e1_d817e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azy1665702712971__table_d815e1_d816e1_d817e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azy1665702712971__table_d815e1_d816e1_d817e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Max</var> value of the\n                                 <code class=\"ph codeph\">LEN(<var class=\"keyword varname\">Min</var>-<var class=\"keyword varname\">Max</var>)</code>\n                           to the field syntax string.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azy1665702712971__table_d815e1_d816e1_d817e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azy1665702712971__table_d815e1_d816e1_d817e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The fixed length of the field as defined in <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Database\n                              Interface</span> is used.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"azy1665702712971__section_z5w_w1m_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d937768e136\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"azy1665702712971__p_d98918e1_d98919e1_d98920e1\">Uniface checks data as it is entered. The default is\n            the fixed length of the field defined in the interface definition for the field. There\n            is no maximum if the field has an unlimited variable length (length defined as\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">*</code>).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"azy1665702712971__p_d98921e1_d98922e1_d98923e1\">If the field supports subfields, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Maximum\n               Field Length</span> specifies the maximum number of characters allowed for each\n            subfield, excluding separators.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"azy1665702712971__section_t42_y1m_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d937768e154\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"azy1665702712971__ul_qfh_z1m_qwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"azy1665702712971__li_d3812e1_d3813e1_d3814e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bbr1665702712405.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bbr1665702712405.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field Syntax is a Development Object that defines some validation rules for data entry in the Field, such as the allowed characters, and field display and control attributes, such dimming and auto-jump.\">Modeled Field Syntax</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/enu1665702584272.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Database Interface (Entities)</a><p>This property (also known as the entity interface) determines how the data is mapped to the database.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612046\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612046\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Maximum Field Length Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Maximum Field Length The maximum number of characters allowed for data in this field. Value Description True Sets the Max value of the LEN( Min - Max ) to the field syntax string. False The fixed length of the field as defined in Database Interface is used. Description Uniface checks data as it is entered. The default is the fixed length of the field defined in the interface definition for the field. There is no maximum if the field has an unlimited variable length (length defined as * ). If the field supports subfields, Maximum Field Length specifies the maximum number of characters allowed for each subfield, excluding separators. Applies To Modeled Field Syntax Related Links Database Interface (Entities) This property (also known as the entity interface) determines how the data is mapped to the database. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}